{
    "poem_title": "Christine",
    "author": "Charles-Marie Leconte de Lisle",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1862",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Une étoile d'or là-bas illumine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Le bleu de la nuit, derrière les monts.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "La lune blanchit la verte colline :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "— Pourquoi pleures-tu, petite Christine ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Une étoile d'or là-bas illumine\nLe bleu de la nuit, derrière les monts.\nLa lune blanchit la verte colline :\n— Pourquoi pleures-tu, petite Christine ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "— Mon fiancé dort sous la noire terre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Dans la froide tombe il rêve de nous.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Laissez-moi pleurer, ma peine est amère ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Laissez-moi gémir et veiller, ma mère :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "— Mon fiancé dort sous la noire terre,\nDans la froide tombe il rêve de nous.\nLaissez-moi pleurer, ma peine est amère ;\nLaissez-moi gémir et veiller, ma mère :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "La mère repose, et Christine pleure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Immobile auprès de l'âtre noirci.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Au long tintement de la douzième heure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Un doigt léger frappe à l'humble demeure :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La mère repose, et Christine pleure,\nImmobile auprès de l'âtre noirci.\nAu long tintement de la douzième heure,\nUn doigt léger frappe à l'humble demeure :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "— Tire le verrou, Christine, ouvre vite :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "C'est ton jeune ami, c'est ton fiancé.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Un suaire étroit à peine m'abrite ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "J'ai quitté pour toi, ma chère petite,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "— Tire le verrou, Christine, ouvre vite :\nC'est ton jeune ami, c'est ton fiancé.\nUn suaire étroit à peine m'abrite ;\nJ'ai quitté pour toi, ma chère petite,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Et cœur contre cœur tous deux ils s'unissent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Chaque baiser dure une éternité :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Les baisers d'amour jamais ne finissent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Ils causent longtemps ; mais les heures glissent,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et cœur contre cœur tous deux ils s'unissent.\nChaque baiser dure une éternité :\nLes baisers d'amour jamais ne finissent.\nIls causent longtemps ; mais les heures glissent,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Le coq a chanté, voici l'aube claire ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "L'étoile s'éteint, le ciel est d'argent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "— Adieu, mon amour, souviens-toi, ma chère !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Les morts vont rentrer dans la noire terre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le coq a chanté, voici l'aube claire ;\nL'étoile s'éteint, le ciel est d'argent.\n— Adieu, mon amour, souviens-toi, ma chère !\nLes morts vont rentrer dans la noire terre,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "— O mon fiancé, souffres-tu, dit-elle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Quand le vent d'hiver gémit dans les bois,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Quand la froide pluie aux tombeaux ruisselle ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Pauvre ami, couché dans l'ombre éternelle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "— O mon fiancé, souffres-tu, dit-elle,\nQuand le vent d'hiver gémit dans les bois,\nQuand la froide pluie aux tombeaux ruisselle ?\nPauvre ami, couché dans l'ombre éternelle,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "— Au rire joyeux de ta lèvre rose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Mieux qu'au soleil d'or le pré rougissant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Mon cercueil s'emplit de feuilles de rose ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Mais tes pleurs amers dans ma tombe close",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "— Au rire joyeux de ta lèvre rose,\nMieux qu'au soleil d'or le pré rougissant,\nMon cercueil s'emplit de feuilles de rose ;\nMais tes pleurs amers dans ma tombe close"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Ne pleure jamais ! Ici-bas tout cesse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Mais le vrai bonheur nous attend au ciel.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Si tu m'as aimé, garde ma promesse :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Dieu nous rendra tout, amour et jeunesse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ne pleure jamais ! Ici-bas tout cesse,\nMais le vrai bonheur nous attend au ciel.\nSi tu m'as aimé, garde ma promesse :\nDieu nous rendra tout, amour et jeunesse,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "— Non ! je t'ai donné ma foi virginale ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Pour me suivre aussi, ne mourrais-tu pas ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Non ! je veux dormir ma nuit nuptiale,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Blanche, à tes côtés, sous la lune pâle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "— Non ! je t'ai donné ma foi virginale ;\nPour me suivre aussi, ne mourrais-tu pas ?\nNon ! je veux dormir ma nuit nuptiale,\nBlanche, à tes côtés, sous la lune pâle,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Lui ne répond rien. Il marche et la guide.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "A l'horizon bleu le soleil paraît.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Ils hâtent alors leur course rapide,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Et vont, traversant sur la mousse humide",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Lui ne répond rien. Il marche et la guide.\nA l'horizon bleu le soleil paraît.\nIls hâtent alors leur course rapide,\nEt vont, traversant sur la mousse humide"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Voici les pins noirs du vieux cimetière.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "— Adieu, quitte-moi, reprends ton chemin ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Mon unique amour, entends ma prière ! —",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Mais Elle au tombeau descend la première,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Voici les pins noirs du vieux cimetière.\n— Adieu, quitte-moi, reprends ton chemin ;\nMon unique amour, entends ma prière ! —\nMais Elle au tombeau descend la première,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Et, depuis ce jour, sous la croix de cuivre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Dans la même tombe ils dorment tous deux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "O sommeil divin dont le charme enivre !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Ils aiment toujours. Heureux qui peut vivre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et, depuis ce jour, sous la croix de cuivre,\nDans la même tombe ils dorment tous deux.\nO sommeil divin dont le charme enivre !\nIls aiment toujours. Heureux qui peut vivre"
        }
    ],
    "corpus": "mel"
